{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbc1ed096-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2313"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2313"},"text":"§ 2313.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Transfer of functions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The President is authorized to delegate the duties and responsibilities placed on the Commission by this chapter to such other agencies of the United States Government as are reasonably qualified to perform those duties and responsibilities. The President may delegate any or all of the duties and responsibilities of the Commission in the operation of the communities to such other agencies of the United States Government that are reasonably qualified to perform those duties and responsibilities. The Commission shall retain no financing duties and responsibilities.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbc1ed097-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1955-08-04/ch543"},"text":"Aug. 4, 1955, ch. 543","children":[],"tail":", ch. 10, § 101, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/69/482"},"text":"69 Stat. 482","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbc1ed098-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idbc1ed099-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"idbc1ed09a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Atomic Energy Commission abolished and functions transferred by sections 5814 and 5841 of this title. See also Transfer of Functions notes set out under those sections.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"idbc1ed09b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"executiveOrder","id":"idbc1ed09c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Order No. 10657","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Ex. Ord. No. 10657, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1956-02-14"},"text":"Feb. 14, 1956","children":[],"tail":", 21 F.R. 1063, as amended by Ex. Ord. No. 10734, eff. "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1957-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1957","children":[],"tail":", 22 F.R. 8275; Ex. Ord. No. 11105, eff. "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1963-04-18"},"text":"Apr. 18, 1963","children":[],"tail":", 28 F.R. 3909, which related to the transfer of certain functions of the Atomic Energy Commission under this chapter to the Housing and Home Finance Administrator, was revoked by Ex. Ord. No. 12553, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-02-25"},"text":"Feb. 25, 1986","children":[],"tail":", 51 F.R. 7237."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"executiveOrder","id":"idbc1ed09d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Order No. 11105","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Ex. Ord. No. 11105, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1963-04-18"},"text":"Apr. 18, 1963","children":[],"tail":", 28 F.R. 3909, which provided for the transfer of certain functions of the Atomic Energy Commission under th